                <ul>
                    <li><b>Height:</b> 25 feet</li>
                    <li><b>Design:</b> A blend of colonial and indigenous styles</li>
                    <li><b>Clock:</b> Meticulously maintained, functional timepiece</li>
                </ul>
                <p>The tower stands as a functional and aesthetic monument, with its clock still accurately marking the passage of time. The chimes of the clock echo through the streets, adding a unique charm to the city's ambiance.</p>
                <h3 class="my-3">Surroundings</h3>
                <p>The area around the Ghanta Ghar is bustling with activity, featuring:</p>
                <ul>
