                <p>The Ghanta Ghar holds a special place in the hearts of Bhagalpur's residents. It serves as a gathering spot for celebrations, rallies, and community events, reflecting the resilience and spirit of the people. The tower has been a witness to numerous historical and cultural events in the city.</p>
                <h3 class="my-3">Preservation Efforts</h3>
                <p>Both government and non-government organizations, including the Indian National Trust for Art and Cultural Heritage (INTACH), are actively involved in preserving this historic monument. Recent renovation work has added a fountain to enhance the aesthetic appeal of the tower.</p>
